# Dezain — Walkthrough

## What Was Built

A complete AI-powered pipeline that converts **Figma designs → React + TypeScript + TailwindCSS** components.

### Architecture

```mermaid
graph LR
    A[Figma API] --> B[Figma Client]
    B --> C[Design Parser]
    C --> D[Intermediate Representation]
    D --> E[LLM Orchestrator]
    F[Design System Registry] --> E
    E --> G[Generated .tsx Files]
    G --> H[Validator]
    H --> I[Output Directory]
```

### Project Structure

| Directory | Purpose |
|---|---|
| `dezain/figma/` | Figma API client + JSON → IR parser |
| `dezain/design_system/` | Component registry + Tailwind token mapping |
| `dezain/generator/` | LLM orchestrator, prompt templates, file writer |
| `dezain/validation/` | Post-generation code validation |
| `dezain/cli.py` | Typer CLI (`dezain generate`, `dezain init`) |
| `dezain/pipeline.py` | Main pipeline orchestration |
| `tests/` | 76 tests across 8 test modules |
| `samples/` | Sample Figma API response for demo mode |

