## How to Use

### Quick Start
```bash
# Clone & setup
cd Dezain
python -m venv desain-venv
desain-venv\Scripts\activate   # Windows
pip install -e ".[dev]"

# Initialize config
dezain init

# Demo mode (no Figma token needed)
dezain generate --sample

# With Figma
cp .env.example .env
# Edit .env with your tokens
dezain generate --file-url "https://figma.com/file/..."
```

### Docker
```bash
docker compose up dezain          # With OpenAI
docker compose --profile local-llm up  # With Ollama
```

